**From auth.controller.ts:**
```typescript
if (!validateEmail(email, true)) {
  // ...
}
// ...
if (!validateEmail(email, false)) {
  // ...
}
```

This is calling `validateEmail(email, true)` and `validateEmail(email, false)` with positional arguments. But the new signature expects an options object `validateEmail(opts: ValidateEmailOptions)`.

